<div class="bibEntry"><p class="bib">276. Franz, Carl. ColorMe Macho. Santa Fe, NM: John Muir, 1985. 112 pp. B/W illus., color illus. </p><p class="annot">This book on male apparel burlesques the topics and illustrations inColor Me Beautiful by Carol Jackson. Chapter topics range from “Machismo: The Myth and the Majesty” to “Your Closet: Heart Of Darkness.” The author claims that the task of producing the text and the contrived photographs occupied a team of eight consultants and designers, all of whom may be fictional. </p></div>
